<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَعَنْهُ:</span> عَلَيْهِ الْفِدْيَةُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلَهُ أَنْ يَخْتَضِبَ <span class="c2">(١)</span> بِالْحِنَّاءِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَقَلِيلُ اللُّبْسِ وَالطِّيبِ وَكَثيرُهُ سَوَاءٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَإذَا احْتَاجَ إِلَى فِعْلِ شَيْءٍ مِنَ الْمَحْظُوراتِ، جَازَ لَهُ ذلِكَ، وعَلَيْهِ الْفِدْيَةُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في "ط": "يخطب".</p> </div>